fm: string baseNeg2(int N) {         if (N == 0 || N == 1)             return to_string(N);         vector<int> res;         while (N) {             res.push_back(N & 1);             N = -(N >> 1);         }         string ret;         for (int i = res.size() - 1; i >= 0; --i)             ret += to_string(res[i]);         return ret;     }

fm: vector<bool> prefixesDivBy5(vector<int> &A) {         int sum = 0;         vector<bool> ret(A.size(), false);         for (int i = 0; i < A.size(); ++i) {             sum = (sum * 2 + A[i]) % 5;             ret[i] = sum == 0 ? true : false;         }         return ret;     }

fm: vector<int> nextLargerNodes(ListNode *head) {         vector<int> s;         while (head) {             s.push_back(head->val);             head = head->next;         }         int n = s.size();         stack<int> temp;         vector<int> ret(n, 0);         for (int i = n - 1; i >= 0; --i) {             while (!temp.empty() && temp.top() <= s[i])                 temp.pop();             ret[i] = temp.empty() ? 0 : temp.top();             temp.push(s[i]);         }         return ret;     }
